              <h2 style="color: #128757;font-weight:700;">Mango "Nice" Cream</h2>
              <p>Made with three native flavors of the tropics, this super-easy mango "nice" cream brings the beach right to you. Joining the namesake fruit are banana and cashew in the form of <a href="/collections/all/products/unsweetened-milked-cashews">Elmhurst Unsweetened Milked Cashews</a>™. All you need is a blender! You can mix things up further by using any Elmhurst plant milk – for instance <a href="/collections/all/products/unsweetened-milked-walnuts">Unsweetened Milked Walnuts</a>™.</p>
